message:
Copilot live-turn p99 latency for ${CUSTOMER_LABEL} is above 30s for 15 minutes.

Likely causes (in order): Anthropic upstream (check status.anthropic.com), Salesforce callout slowness (look at @msg:soql_completed durations), Vercel cold starts (compare to deploy times). The cost-cap doesn't trip until ~$0.30/turn so a slow turn often means a runaway tool loop — pull the trace and inspect the @tool_count + @iterations fields.

Runbook: docs/runbook.md §11. 

@oncall-${CUSTOMER_LABEL}
